item.title: stminsights
item.description: his app enables interactive validation, interpretation and visualization of structural topic models from the ‘stm’ package by Roberts and others (2014) doi:10.1111/ajps.12103. It also includes helper functions for model diagnostics and extracting data from effect estimates.
